      <title>埃及维持历史高利率，重点关注抑制通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/egypt-holds-record-high-rate-to-keep-lid-on-slowing-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及连续第二次会议将利率维持在历史最高水平，以确保在货币大幅贬值后通胀继续放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/egypt-holds-record-high-rate-to-keep-lid-on-slowing-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
